<p><b>Study skills</b> and <b>study strategies</b> are abilities and approaches applied to learning. They are generally critical to success in school<sup id="cite_ref-eric1_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-eric1-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>, are considered essential for acquiring good grades, and they are useful for learning throughout one's life, in support of career and personal interests.</p>
<p>They include removing distractions, <a href="/wiki/Time_management" title="Time management">time management</a> and <a href="/wiki/Notetaking" title="Notetaking">notetaking</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
