<p><a name="Resource_availability" id="Resource_availability"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Study_skills&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Resource availability">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Resource availability</span></h2>
<p>Educational institutions often offer student counseling, or provide resources for improving study skills. <sup id="cite_ref-vatech1_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-vatech1-2" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup> There are a vast number of resources marketed as study skills. The learning methods offered for sale range from <a href="/wiki/Time_management" title="Time management">how to manage time</a>, to <a href="/wiki/Notetaking" title="Notetaking">notetaking</a>, to <a href="/wiki/Cognitive_enhancers" title="Cognitive enhancers" class="mw-redirect">smart drugs and nutrients</a> for improving performance during study. <sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-3" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p><a name="Types_of_study_skills" id="Types_of_study_skills"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Study_skills&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Types of study skills">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Types of study skills</span></h2>
